comment:
* Lightweight identity hash table which maps objects to replacement
     * objects.

methods.name: void assign(Object obj, Object rep)
methods.comment: * Enters mapping from object to replacement object.

methods.name: Object lookup(Object obj)
methods.comment:
* Looks up and returns replacement for given object.  If no
         * replacement is found, returns the lookup object itself.

methods.name: void clear()
methods.comment: * Resets table to its initial (empty) state.

methods.name: int size()
methods.comment: * Returns the number of mappings currently in table.
